title: Lee Sin buffs
body:
Lee Sin
Sonic Wave / Resonating Strike (Q)
Sonic Wave damage increased from 50/75/100/125/150 to 50/80/110/140/170
Resonating Strike damage increased from 50/75/100/125/150 to 50/80/110/140/170

And all {{champion:64}} can do is hit Q for more damage
Talk about Skill

replies.body: his q should be a execute if they are at 80% hp or lower since hes fun to watch
